Localization.Name: Ranta Dung
Localization.Description: A dry cube-shaped dung that comes from a large isopod-like crustacean known as a Ranta. It has recently been discovered that the dung contains a unique bacterial biome that helps the Ranta process and digest minerals and some researches are hopeful will lead to industrial or medical innovations.
